:"Jsqbn225Ssey2IpZnnpmOQ","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"77","text":"ECO es gold standard para descartar (hidronefrosis)","guid":"2ar63hq0ToiJ7kdV-F1hjw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"0","text":"EVALUACIÓN EN URGENCIAS","guid":"hfThqZSxSHqURKtfezibYg","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"ANAMNESIS ESENCIAL","guid":"TKFQ5714QS2Hs1FHV3W3Tg","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"Historia de ERC conocida (valor basal Cr)","guid":"szQSVH6IT0Wzi4Pp8lHAGA","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"Ingesta hídrica reciente","guid":"goROUjDjQTCmZUs2RbBvBw","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"89","text":"Pérdidas (diarrea, vómitos, sudoración, hemorragia)","guid":"EyVCwnn2TumiErDl0n-IRw","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"89","text":"Fármacos nuevos o dosis ajustadas (semanas previas)","guid":"8frBb52fSjC0Dkr82b2lHg","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"89","text":"Contraste yodado reciente (TC, angiografía)","guid":"-1xqRePwQOCw2Yl5bS_cEg","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"89","text":"Síntomas urinarios (disuria, hematuria, tenesmo, nicturia)","guid":"s08m_iCnQnaBg8JX6a1L8A","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"89","text":"Fiebre, lesiones cutáneas, artralgias (vasculitis)","guid":"vnkMe6i-TPeoaPU_mpjJBA","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"89","text":"Trauma reciente (rabdomiolisis)","guid":"PyffZA7jSI2NWvgIo3lTsg","children":[]}]},{"id":"98","parent":"88","text":"EXAMEN FÍSICO ORIENTADO","guid":"2bJNlKLVTpKJ95PbVkmRHw","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"Estado hemodinámico → PA, FC, llene capilar, PVC clínica","guid":"P6iCjXcXTy-YHu127gonvQ","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"98","text":"Signos de hipovolemia → mucosas secas, turgor, IY aplanada","guid":"k8SgXRktRhmlmyviY7Jh7Q","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"98","text":"Signos de sobrecarga → crepitantes, edema, IY distendida, S3","guid":"RPhSK-QCT9mMUvZBuZw6XQ","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"98","text":"Globo vesical palpable","guid":"nnzS-ZJ4Ts2no2FZcRDlSQ","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"98","text":"Tacto rectal → próstata, fecalomas","guid":"zGyvzSMoR0ydozapURKXmQ","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"98","text":"Rash, púrpura, livedo (vasculitis, colesterol)","guid":"o-C7og-VQvmddKuJ-gGF6A","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"98","text":"Palpación abdominal → masas, soplos","guid":"ersohAEjStaLcnAownH1Ew","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"98","text":"Examen neurológico → asterixis, encefalopatía urémica","guid":"GLZoTdQwRJqHbPKpr0vRbA","children":[]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"88","text":"LABORATORIO INICIAL","guid":"byEm_LVTRCyVFSAVsmfFJg","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"BUN, creatinina serial","guid":"3R3OI42QTwqA7OEKCmWc3Q","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"107","text":"Electrolitos → K+, Na+, Cl-, HCO3-","guid":"GD2OHsGGRu-npv0-IelMcA","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"107","text":"Gasometría arterial → acidosis metabólica","guid":"duOhGaQ7SAeudZqmKGJ6CQ","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"107","text":"Hemograma completo","guid":"ydVzqujxSVKOqLQtxYz_sg","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"107","text":"Calcio, fósforo, magnesio","guid":"ho_c2HFkQRK5XeZWXV3cLQ","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"107","text":"Albúmina","guid":"w8GG02eARMekPKOQxJHSdQ","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"107","text":"LDH, CK (sospecha rabdomiolisis si CK >5000)","guid":"zhCa4beaTPyfmAFyK4n_7A","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"107","text":"Perfil hepático","guid":"T0L6MlImQwu8vQcx8Ur0Xw","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"107","text":"Orina completa con sedimento","guid":"C974KLc5ToKUoQeU7I6vBg","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"Proteinuria, hematuria, leucocituria","guid":"9NEOPGTgSw6zFjccI-wXXg","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"116","text":"Cilindros granulosos pardos → NTA","guid":"FCp7FrUWSjiFf0a-Snoq6Q","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"116","text":"Cilindros hemáticos → GN","guid":"CRDGAyfuRim4I2_WB65U_A","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"116","text":"Cilindros leucocitarios → NIA, pielonefritis","guid":"obLBZ_4IQkyYLRGA2EJwOQ","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"116","text":"Eosinofiluria → NIA alérgica","guid":"Z-P6sGLoQ6emv4pyg-Vrhg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"88","text":"ÍNDICES URINARIOS","guid":"QDBSf-1_TUmEoedPzyNXRA","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"FeNa (sin diuréticos) = (Na urinario × Cr plasma) / (Na plasma × Cr urinario) × 100","guid":"s32jo-qSR2KwqXtD99CePg","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"<1% → PRE-RENAL","guid":"LR4htDq8Q-OWHqHsIhydOg","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"123","text":">2% → NTA / INTRÍNSECA","guid":"0jyq9s3RRaKqvkgJ-W5xGg","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"123","text":"1-2% → indeterminado","guid":"dPy4z_VySjKCXyIfUsPRXg","children":[]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"122","text":"FeUrea (con diuréticos) = (Urea urinaria × Cr plasma) / (Urea plasma × Cr urinario) × 100","guid":"WuvYBve9RBG2iMnOxy2ApA","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"<35% → PRE-RENAL","guid":"CqrfMXVkT9-GBg3kp2rstQ","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"127","text":">50% → NTA","guid":"bQ2NbhvsSDmGSZZ2uSsrEg","children":[]}]},{"id":"130","parent":"122","text":"Densidad urinaria >1020 → orina concentrada (pre-renal)","guid":"nwQFuHxMRwyXt0VZOBJ1cQ","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"122","text":"Osmolaridad urinaria >500 mOsm/kg → pre-renal","guid":"VJcjTCRWRn20At-uG_EC7g","children":[]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"88","text":"IMAGEN","guid":"inXFnG5fRxeKzjhL3_IOSg","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"Ecografía renal → PRIMERA LÍNEA en urgencias","guid":"k3IMJ4xWR2mO14RNQ5P40A","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"Descarta uropatía obstructiva (hidronefrosis)","guid":"qVboK1-kTh6boA729GbL-g","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"Tamaño riñones (reducidos → ERC previa)","guid":"FzUkRvkgRdCn6ohua023aw","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"Ecogenicidad cortical","guid":"I4_-L_0WSoasuBRbpGwpXw","children":[]}]},{"id":"137","parent":"132","text":"TC sin contraste → si sospecha litiasis, masas, retroperitoneo","guid":"97pOCQtZQ8K_mEYAQqqxvQ","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"132","text":"RM con gadolinio → EVITAR en AKI severa (riesgo fibrosis sistémica nefrogénica)","guid":"o9JCmbr0SACf3Z0mi3U-GA","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"132","text":"Biopsia renal → si sospecha glomerulopatía, NIA, vasculitis y pronóstico incierto","guid":"mbnM-GZuTg6QngrjZUFSTA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"0","text":"LR DIAGNOSTICOS","guid":"lDkvCbycSriXGdHrdx81Rw","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"HALLAZGOS CLINICOS (cabecera)","guid":"HzfYl9wvQUyvm3edCWT-hQ","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"Hipotension ortostatica postural (>20 mmHg sistolica) -> LR+ 1.5-3 -> LR- NR -> PMID:10086438","guid":"l6Hm4Nz9QAiWd1Zwc8Fivg","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"Sed extrema en paciente alerta -> LR+ 2.8 -> LR- NR -> PMID:10086438","guid":"DNEOptz8TuS92JWd6hmnGg","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"141","text":"Lengua surcada / seca -> LR+ 2.0 -> LR- NR -> PMID:10086438","guid":"PwkrzsocRWm5BC8Xj2uamw","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"141","text":"Axilas secas -> LR+ 2.8 -> LR- NR -> PMID:10086438","guid":"AXYxCGAZSYKDIBpvwdNLOw","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"141","text":"Mucosas orales secas -> LR+ 2.0 -> LR- NR -> PMID:10086438","guid":"RWw4OgZbQAuK-rlOybQVCg","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"141","text":"Globo vesical palpable + anuria -> [definitorio post-renal]","guid":"jyaLwEO4SQahqfLoDDzn8A","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"141","text":"Estertores + IY + S3 (sobrecarga -> sindrome cardiorenal) -> combinacion alta probabilidad","guid":"6pwr-E2HQKSMYbQB_DPigA","children":[]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"140","text":"HALLAZGOS LABORATORIO","guid":"rA0KjUquRYm64YeCsFG_yQ","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"FeNa <1 por ciento (sin diureticos, para pre-renal) -> LR+ 4.7 -> LR- 0.27 -> PMID:666184","guid":"TpxprXegRGKxLlde78Ge_A","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"FeNa >2 por ciento (para NTA/intrinseca) -> LR+ 2.5 -> LR- 0.4 -> PMID:666184","guid":"_VnmeoPhQO2yW2bdkdbgug","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"149","text":"FeUrea <35 por ciento (pre-renal con diureticos) -> LR+ ~5 -> LR- 0.5 -> PMID:12427149","guid":"ToyulJLFQ86K3MfnF0tc0Q","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"149","text":"BUN/Cr ratio >20 (pre-renal) -> LR+ ~4 -> LR- 0.5 -> (texto clasico Rose BD)","guid":"wVGvlGhdRTi8Qa-tbeQxcg","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"149","text":"Cilindros granulosos pardos en sedimento -> apoya NTA","guid":"KDxqXTraRv-4DoaCaki7Ig","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"149","text":"Cilindros hematicos -> apoya GN","guid":"K7XHCni9Sau6FW40tUxjNw","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"149","text":"Eosinofiluria (azul de metileno o Hansel) -> apoya NIA (S baja)","guid":"GbfmvpW0Sxm70w9SmznH5A","children":[]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"140","text":"HALLAZGOS IMAGEN","guid":"axcmhXReR3a52iDhS_LFmQ","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"POCUS con colapso VCI >50 por ciento con inspiracion (hipovolemia) -> LR+ ~4 -> LR- ~0.4 -> PMID:19556029","guid":"C742yJj8QxeGOVTOKmbbKQ","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"157","text":"POCUS con VCI pletorica sin variacion (sobrecarga) -> apoya sobrecarga","guid":"AysnceKvSnSxQZNxBFPDKw","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"157","text":"Ecografia renal con hidronefrosis (post-renal) -> Sens 98% Esp 78% -> PMID:21098348","guid":"LoAVF_xCQwuFGLz82foCJA","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"157","text":"Resistivity index >0.7 -> apoya intrinseca (variable por experiencia)","guid":"1G9e7DvAQbWH59aTk-sP8w","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"140","text":"SCORE / REGLA CLINICA","guid":"RJC88X2qS0e3r84rPjhKGQ","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"Criterios KDIGO 2012 (cualquiera de 3) -> [definitorios IRA] -> PMID:25949596","guid":"YDxyh_17RL-DPKecqE6epA","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"Nephrocheck (TIMP2 x IGFBP7) >0.3 -> marcador temprano IRA en UCI","guid":"wvQQibQDQxqp3ChkMjPt7g","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"162","text":"CNAS (Contrast-induced Nephropathy) -> riesgo CIN pre-procedimiento","guid":"3_sm0FXYQ-2QvuQHXfV6Yg","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"140","text":"INTERPRETACION","guid":"3zDvPkobQMyntw5Uz_mcxA","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"LR+ >10 o LR- <0.1 -> cambio GRANDE","guid":"HKD2zr8HTEaRcBn1MEi0yQ","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"LR+ 5-10 o LR- 0.1-0.2 -> cambio MODERADO","guid":"A8kKdJdpTgqQpM8gropm2Q","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"166","text":"LR+ 2-5 o LR- 0.2-0.5 -> cambio pequeno pero significativo","guid":"GN0I6_ofQCu_BS18oJhfLw","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"166","text":"En AM la creatinina puede subestimar deterioro -> sospecha clinica aunque valores parezcan estables","guid":"o2PzPlHtQZOfI7lsRjCddQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"0","text":"MANEJO EN URGENCIAS","guid":"N3IyrIsEQ16Hj3TboEWQGg","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"EVALUACIÓN HEMODINÁMICA Y VOLEMIA","guid":"CDS3DoPGTZGcZuifqLbQPQ","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"Hipovolemia → reposición cristaloides (balanceados > SF 0.9% si gran volumen)","guid":"e1lcMWzPRC-y15EqYqjK5Q","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"172","text":"Sobrecarga → restricción hídrica + diuréticos de asa","guid":"2hp3Wdi7RcCgbfvnwZy9Mg","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"172","text":"Shock → resolución de causa primaria (séptico, cardiogénico, obstructivo, hipovolémico)","guid":"C_AuSTkYSD-LbS7bKp1oFA","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"171","text":"SUSPENDER NEFROTÓXICOS","guid":"sm29Z0WOTBCchbDOA1gqLg","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"AINEs","guid":"GIEv8xUlS7eRmCkR1daWcg","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"IECA/ARA2 (si hipovolemia o deterioro agudo)","guid":"GycWKhGyT6-VmmU8LROSxA","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"176","text":"Aminoglucósidos","guid":"-XFuduNETd6QMmS5CGwe9w","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"176","text":"Contraste yodado","guid":"fbTZnIK7QpSZ8pcNau5VKg","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"176","text":"Metformina (suspender, no por nefrotoxicidad directa sino por acidosis láctica)","guid":"spfADkpTS_2-NVPrYWKcgA","children":[]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"171","text":"AJUSTAR FARMACOTERAPIA A FUNCIÓN RENAL","guid":"rlL6QLXjS-OSZq4WNVn5yw","children":[{"id":"183","parent":"182","text":"Revisar TODO fármaco → dosis y frecuencia según eGFR","guid":"Q0wUjdwHQ_mbZgniA3-uPw","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"182","text":"Especial atención → anticoagulantes, antibióticos, antivirales, hipoglicemiantes","guid":"aUQw9fq0SqazFw1k1yiE5w","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"182","text":"Desprescribir lo no esencial (STOPP/START)","guid":"Z3HlNo16TAqAxhPTvHWyYQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"186","parent":"171","text":"CORRECCIÓN ELECTROLÍTICA","guid":"hiMHqB5mRmicyBV6XfZDeA","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"HIPERKALEMIA","guid":"d8rdgCX5SlWdxLabEUSHxA","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"Estabilización miocárdica → gluconato de calcio 10% 10 mL EV","guid":"Hf7d6GhfS2SFOzHb3DvKGA","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"187","text":"Shift intracelular","guid":"XaEw_Ji3RyalnUVifAqrwQ","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"Insulina 10U + glucosa 25g EV","guid":"oeV3ySDGT621iYZuTBwZJg","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"189","text":"Beta-2 agonista (salbutamol nebulizado)","guid":"KUeAX8xaQNWowdTZCKZBNw","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"189","text":"Bicarbonato (si acidosis severa)","guid":"IybUBmDIT-G4aRk4E8LfaA","children":[]}]},{"id":"193","parent":"187","text":"Eliminación","guid":"kp_epz50RnSFlhoHZhOH5Q","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"Diuréticos de asa (si diuresis conservada)","guid":"yhklBV90R2mp0spWCWnxnQ","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"Resinas (poliestireno sulfonato, patiromer)","guid":"6rRQsODdS3igcdZLxJylsg","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"193","text":"HEMODIÁLISIS (definitivo)","guid":"wFUUotAlTbicV2Or_qleSA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"186","text":"ACIDOSIS METABÓLICA","guid":"PadRWsJZQkatQnI_JuI9bQ","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"Bicarbonato EV si pH <7.1 o HCO3 <10","guid":"cNfJfAsCTYCLlBx2uvpfag","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"197","text":"Tratar causa subyacente","guid":"MlcpHQMxQG6YroNcfNOzxA","children":[]}]},{"id":"200","parent":"186","text":"HIPO/HIPERNATREMIA","guid":"TLWteOgTRKaOL_F1Ig-KdQ","children":[{"id":"201","parent":"200","text":"Corrección lenta (evitar mielinólisis central pontina)","guid":"cmOn58SpTiCBIrwgvFKwrg","children":[]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"186","text":"HIPOCALCEMIA / HIPERFOSFATEMIA","guid":"_FcWaxe9SkenX2Mu_W0vtQ","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"Quelantes de fósforo si hiperfosfatemia sintomática","guid":"0tvdIlWkQ8iDs40gIRuM_w","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"Calcio EV si tetania o QTc prolongado","guid":"giZ0mc5CSV-tWPBwJ_FooQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"205","parent":"171","text":"RESOLUCIÓN DE OBSTRUCCIÓN","guid":"iNipGMgTSI63plHtPaGuhg","children":[{"id":"206","parent":"205","text":"Sondaje vesical → globo vesical","guid":"bqu62xEUT2eKsPBZ0q5ReQ","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"205","text":"Nefrostomía percutánea bilateral → obstrucción ureteral","guid":"eb7xE1GURdG0p0TpMdeeCQ","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"205","text":"Catéter doble J → obstrucción ureteral unilateral o parcial","guid":"1JtnZVXkSKqkAID0dmvuGQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"209","parent":"171","text":"MANEJO ETIOLÓGICO ESPECÍFICO","guid":"3fYl-KIoSMOaqsdNjYTapg","children":[{"id":"210","parent":"209","text":"Sepsis → control foco + antibiótico + resucitación","guid":"QYoBRAFORNCDjbiDR8oTAw","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"209","text":"Rabdomiolisis → hidratación abundante (250-500 mL/h), objetivo diuresis 200-300 mL/h, considerar alcalinización","guid":"5ySi8y7PS3KRH9IwyRIVDw","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"209","text":"NIA → retiro del fármaco causante, corticoides en casos severos","guid":"SrxaSx8kROGczY84rf7IdA","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"209","text":"GN rápidamente progresiva → inmunosupresión urgente (pulsos de metilprednisolona, ciclofosfamida, rituximab)","guid":"g2h3btURSduTTtdPwKsdVQ","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"209","text":"Síndrome hepatorenal → albúmina + terlipresina / noradrenalina","guid":"5UsEVrmpTZucyGguG1jHdg","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"209","text":"MAT → plasmaféresis urgente","guid":"c33lh6eOQYGUN2SD21_Dxg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"216","parent":"0","text":"INDICACIONES DE TERAPIA DE REEMPLAZO RENAL (AEIOU)","guid":"LNR_nzLISNS5AHQ2zvWYTg","children":[{"id":"217","parent":"216","text":"A → ACIDOSIS severa refractaria (pH <7.1 con bicarbonato insuficiente)","guid":"Tto1Gp7HR4iKxAuzPK039g","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"216","text":"E → ELECTROLITOS (hiperkalemia >6.5 refractaria, hipernatremia severa)","guid":"Wdz2WDmDQPiRUnDamyr3DQ","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"216","text":"I → INTOXICACIONES (metanol, etilenglicol, litio, salicilatos, metformina con acidosis láctica)","guid":"2wF1aqiBS_-zPJoQYiTbbA","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"216","text":"O → OVERLOAD de volumen refractario a diuréticos (edema agudo pulmón)","guid":"Hp2p8NeUSoCywo92lPBnvg","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"216","text":"U → UREMIA sintomática (encefalopatía, pericarditis, sangrado urémico)","guid":"ZZOzwphvSOGjuLlXcvJ7ZQ","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"216","text":"MODALIDADES","guid":"wEtpUcF5TfK28eGEJEFh2w","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"Hemodiálisis intermitente → rápida, estable hemodinámicamente","guid":"mEQgwlRpQHeGYke7c7e6UQ","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"222","text":"Hemofiltración continua (CVVHDF) → paciente inestable en UCI","guid":"L8fvJTgZSROOvSrH4LoPiw","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"222","text":"Diálisis peritoneal → menos frecuente en agudo","guid":"u6cI3EfTT3KUEEKhr7SulQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"226","parent":"0","text":"CONSIDERACIONES GERIÁTRICAS","guid":"4UP1WYyOTlGTUiPhiUaOyg","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"FRAGILIDAD Y PRONÓSTICO","guid":"Td8_UEukQTKa9LP_Yegeeg","children":[{"id":"228","parent":"227","text":"CFS ≥5 → peor supervivencia post-IRA","guid":"fFUt9h7OTj6wTS-Io3RMSw","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"227","text":"Dependencia funcional pre-IRA → predictor fuerte de mortalidad","guid":"iB5FT41zRCK3XtEaWAFTEQ","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"227","text":"Sarcopenia → recuperación funcional lenta o incompleta","guid":"MMLsFHieTAqPwnzxmUX7JA","children":[]}]},{"id":"231","parent":"226","text":"DECISIÓN DE TRR EN AM FRÁGIL","guid":"-GG6jiDMSDyeSGg2fxLzRA","children":[{"id":"232","parent":"231","text":"NO es automática — evaluación individual","guid":"wbokvX2dTR60GLhE9APdBg","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"231","text":"Factores → expectativa de vida, voluntades anticipadas, calidad de vida previa","guid":"dBvUJZw9SKSJ-8H7KDEohg","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"231","text":"Proporcionalidad terapéutica → considerar trial limitado de TRR","guid":"w-lnCwI1RLqLsTxMbn2KQw","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"231","text":"Involucrar a familia y paciente en decisión compartida","guid":"GQs5Ru-iSh-0JGUTVzwhFg","children":[]}]},{"id":"236","parent":"226","text":"PREVENCIÓN","guid":"XjJ-pCULSAuMkRxAun3WPw","children":[{"id":"237","parent":"236","text":"Evitar tríada AINEs + IECA/ARA2 + diurético","guid":"5W3oOKxaQ-e0UYTBRGxMEQ","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"236","text":"Hidratación adecuada pre/post contraste (salino isotónico)","guid":"RJqP64y4THyQ4AnlfZu8Aw","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"236","text":"Revisión farmacológica al ingreso (deprescribir)","guid":"oZBpf_EtQfO0LVADjrsxgA","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"236","text":"Monitoreo de diuresis en hospitalizados de riesgo","guid":"GYchiHq6SkeajCwlSN9myQ","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"236","text":"Nutrición adecuada (no restringir proteínas agresivamente excepto en fase específica)","guid":"TLHo2FqESV-W5V2NESYyZg","children":[]}]},{"id":"242","parent":"226","text":"SÍNDROME POST-IRA","guid":"ydAZeK80T56TLw2lMNLptQ","children":[{"id":"243","parent":"242","text":"Mayor riesgo de ERC progresiva a 1-5 años","guid":"DSE3uUU2Sg-YdV7LinsJfw","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"242","text":"Seguimiento nefrológico post-alta obligatorio","guid":"AKBbadbMRc6yjwzgkp7ZRQ","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"242","text":"Ajuste medicación crónica según nueva función renal","guid":"T811rzSXRmG_RPMmKkuqiA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"246","parent":"0","text":"ALGORITMO RESUMEN URGENCIAS","guid":"OQ6h5AFTQKyjp3dGiMGKQQ","children":[{"id":"247","parent":"246","text":"1. Confirmar AKI por KDIGO (Cr, diuresis)","guid":"VVkb7mtORpuEy6QxNlP_Hg","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"246","text":"2. Estadificar (1-3)","guid":"9k2npcm7TB69MdCO3iINlg","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"246","text":"3. Evaluar volemia → hipo vs euvolemia vs sobrecarga","guid":"CBIKQPF7R6ywPC1sprxPuQ","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"246","text":"4. Descartar obstrucción (eco urgente)","guid":"l0hukZ__Qly4hiBh02vgsw","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"246","text":"5. Revisar fármacos → suspender nefrotóxicos","guid":"aPM0ULt9RdGgdScsF5D-Sw","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"246","text":"6. Laboratorio completo + sedimento urinario + FeNa/FeUrea","guid":"keL_qAZcQ0m1T4Z-TfiiUA","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"246","text":"7. Tratar causa específica","guid":"rqKpausFT7GUVabzBl9DFw","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"246","text":"8. Manejar complicaciones (K+, acidosis, sobrecarga)","guid":"jIfpxGsRSz67MPIpOguyNA","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"246","text":"9. Indicaciones AEIOU → TRR","guid":"OWSYxgcjS_6ZM7ylxKIWNg","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"246","text":"10. En AM frágil → evaluación de proporcionalidad","guid":"dQghSfT4Q2GQZLClEOlayw","children":[]}]},{"id":"257","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas","guid":"TORIwuF0Tz2iBOTAbFzWbQ","children":[{"id":"258","parent":"257","text":"Creatinina basal en AM puede sobreestimar VFG → usar CKD-EPI","guid":"JhAIehERTqyumT-mfmoWXA","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"257","text":"TRÍADA LETAL → AINEs + IECA/ARA2 + diurético en AM deshidratado","guid":"0QegYJa-S-GulDQwa2J9tA","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"257","text":"Globo vesical → SIEMPRE tacto rectal y eco bedside en anuria aguda","guid":"qQXCXwZvSaiPKQBOYUzC-Q","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"257","text":"FeNa <1% → pre-renal; FeUrea <35% si diurético presente","guid":"Hxy9YWm4RhyJosxA27rNfA","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"257","text":"AM con IRA inexplicada → pensar en NIA por fármacos (IBP, ATB, alopurinol)","guid":"RPiGfWN3Qiu3RVXpBdc9gA","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"257","text":"Rabdomiolisis → hidratar temprano y abundante, diuresis 200-300 mL/h","guid":"vCeWrd2vRoexXWv5cWloAA","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"257","text":"NO retrasar TRR por edad — evaluar función, no cronología","guid":"sdsNA-f1Q9m9ebo7_pDnEQ","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"257","text":"Delirium en IRA → buscar uremia, acidosis, hiponatremia, sobrecarga","guid":"l5BLP-XeQLaL69W6R62dhA","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"257","text":"Contraste yodado → pre-hidratar con salino isotónico, minimizar dosis","guid":"QrR1Y27jQpquEBT-g7UWLw","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"257","text":"Metformina en IRA → suspender por riesgo acidosis láctica, no por nefrotoxicidad","guid":"-HKYMVidT_OJV4g5AkymfA","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"257","text":"Referencias","guid":"ppwLkCqtTeCNZm4rwlROww","children":[{"id":"269","parent":"268","text":"1. KDIGO Clinical Practice Guideline for Acute Kidney Injury. Kidney Int Suppl. 2012;2(1):1-138. PMID:25949596","guid":"P5Z_O4WQQmS5OelbZBY4wg","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"268","text":"2. Miller TR et al. Urinary diagnostic indices in acute renal failure: a prospective study. Ann Intern Med. 1978;89(1):47-50. PMID:666184","guid":"wW-3TQZxTnS0yDartfuttQ","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"268","text":"3. Carvounis CP et al. Significance of the fractional excretion of urea in the differential diagnosis of acute renal failure. Kidney Int. 2002;62(6):2223-9. PMID:12427149","guid":"zGhtdamLQHm6-KMrG9kh1w","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"268","text":"4. McGee S, Abernethy WB, Simel DL. Is this patient hypovolemic? JAMA. 1999;281(11):1022-1029. PMID:10086438","guid":"quMnlE4WQ4-HvBVRSNGLIQ","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"268","text":"5. Licurse A et al. Renal ultrasonography in the evaluation of acute kidney injury: developing a risk stratification framework. Arch Intern Med. 2010;170(21):1900-7. PMID:21098348","guid":"4zzYKygKT_urDf5WefVykQ","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"268","text":"6. Nagdev AD et al. Emergency department bedside ultrasonographic measurement of the caval index. Ann Emerg Med. 2010;55(3):290-5. PMID:19556029","guid":"EiRnclxuR6e-iOP1DxqRUA","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"268","text":"7. Ostermann M, Joannidis M. Acute kidney injury 2016: diagnosis and diagnostic workup. Crit Care. 2016;20:299. PMID:27670788","guid":"2d4RwijeQkODMDmd2m-9cw","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"268","text":"8. Bellomo R, Kellum JA, Ronco C. Acute kidney injury. Lancet. 2012;380(9843):756-66. PMID:22617274","guid":"rKCcvn0URaKWlPlJTlcSVQ","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"268","text":"9. Ronco C, Bellomo R, Kellum JA. Acute kidney injury. Lancet. 2019;394(10212):1949-64. PMID:31777389","guid":"DeSV_k_VSmOhQjPxx2uicQ","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":277,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Medicina de Urgencia","folder":"MUE - Medicina de Urgencia","filename":"MUE_IRA_Urgencia","id":"map_2509","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"MUE_IRA_Urgencia"}